column8: A Flyknit tongue and heel offer a second-skin fit to deliver stretch and support where you need it most.
Soft, supple leather wraps over the Flyknit for unrivaled touch on the ball. A Fitmesh liner preserves the shape of the boot by preventing stretching as the leather seasons.
